review_blob: Quite good american porter. Smoke chipotle with roasted barley and peated malts dryhopped with chinook. Interesting and well balanced.
Nice stout with chocolate notes, a little bit watery but very drinkable. Just a stout for two a three pints.
Great sour berliner weisse. Fresh hops and citrus smell make an awesome beer,
Berliner weisse with brusnika. First Berliner weisse in Russia. Worth to try. Interesting. Amazing pink color.
